Good progress being made on this new build project in Shepperton. 

Suspended ground floor structure erected and concrete floors laid. The house has been designed to reduce the risk of flooding by constructing the ground floor elevated.

This house will provide a good space to live for a theoretical high flood return period of 100 years.

*Demo & Haul away

*Restore
